[{"title":"Manjaro配置","url":"/2021/06/21/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/","content":"<h2 id=\"初步配置\"><a href=\"#初步配置\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"初步配置\"></a>初步配置</h2><h3 id=\"换源\"><a href=\"#换源\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"换源\"></a>换源</h3><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">su</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 输入密码进入root权限</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman-mirrors -i -c China -m rank</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 排列出manjaro中国开源镜像站并弹窗（注意大小写）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 选择清华大学或者交大的源</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 添加CN-Arch源</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用nano编辑器编辑pacman（包管理器-理解为appstore）配置文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nano /etc/pacman.conf</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 在文件的最后两行加入</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">[archlinuxcn]</span><br><span class=\"line\">Server=https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/archlinuxcn/$arch</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 更新指令</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman -Syy <span class=\"comment\"># 软件包列表更新</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman -S archlinuxcn-keyring <span class=\"comment\"># 导入key</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman -Syu <span class=\"comment\"># 全局更新</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"软件安装\"><a href=\"#软件安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"软件安装\"></a>软件安装</h2><h3 id=\"Chinese-input\"><a href=\"#Chinese-input\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Chinese input\"></a>Chinese input</h3><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 法一</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># installs</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx-im</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx-configtool</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx-googlepinyin</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S fcitx-sunpinyin</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># config</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo vim  ~/.xprofile</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 在末尾添加下方代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\">export QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\">export XMODIFIERS=<span class=\"string\">&quot;@im=fcitx&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#输入法配置完成后重启</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 法二（推荐）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman -S fcitx-im fcitx-configtool manjaro-asian-<span class=\"built_in\">input</span>-support-fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\">pacman -S fcitx-cloudpinyin</span><br><span class=\"line\">exit <span class=\"comment\"># 退回普通用户</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 使用nano编辑器编辑文件，如果文件不存在会自动创建</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">nano ~/.xprofile</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 在末尾添加下方代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">export LC_ALL=zh_CN.UTF-<span class=\"number\">8</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\">export QT_IM_MODULE=fcitx</span><br><span class=\"line\">export XMODIFIERS=“@im=fcitx”</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"QQ\"><a href=\"#QQ\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"QQ\"></a>QQ</h3><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S adobe-source-han-sans-cn-fonts</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S xdotool</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S com.qq.im.deepin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Wechat\"><a href=\"#Wechat\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Wechat\"></a>Wechat</h3><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S yay</span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo pacman -S base-devel</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S deepin-wine-wechat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"网易云音乐\"><a href=\"#网易云音乐\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"网易云音乐\"></a>网易云音乐</h3><figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#　由于官方源和AUR以及yay都删除了网易云依赖的包 qcef ，所以需要我们自己编译安装 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 克隆脚本</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">git clone https://aur.archlinux.org/qcef.git</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 切换到路径</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">cd qcef</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#编译安装</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">makepkg -si</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 注意安装过程中会要求输入密码</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 关于无法输入中文 </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 修改.bash文件</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">sudo nano /opt/netease/netease-cloud-music/netease-cloud-music.bash</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 替换成下方代码</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#!/bin/sh</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">HERE=<span class=\"string\">&quot;$(dirname &quot;</span>$(readlink -f <span class=\"string\">&quot;$&#123;0&#125;&quot;</span>)<span class=\"string\">&quot;)&quot;</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=&quot;$&#123;HERE&#125;&quot;/libs</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># export QT_PLUGIN_PATH=&quot;$&#123;HERE&#125;&quot;/plugins </span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># export QT_QPA_PLATFORM_PLUGIN_PATH=&quot;$&#123;HERE&#125;&quot;/plugins/platforms</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">export XDG_CURRENT_DESKTOP=DDE</span><br><span class=\"line\">export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/usr/lib</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"built_in\">exec</span> <span class=\"string\">&quot;$&#123;HERE&#125;&quot;</span>/netease-cloud-music $@</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h3 id=\"SSR\"><a href=\"#SSR\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"SSR\"></a>SSR</h3>   <figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">Download Qv2ray <span class=\"keyword\">and</span> (AppImage) SSR plugin</span><br><span class=\"line\">chmod +x *.AppInage</span><br><span class=\"line\">mv SSR plugin to /home/$USER/.config/qv2ray/plugins/</span><br><span class=\"line\">Click , Click group, add your links.AppImag</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"WPS\"><a href=\"#WPS\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"WPS\"></a>WPS</h3>   <figure class=\"highlight python\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 安装wps</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S wps-office </span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S ttf-wps-fonts</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">#　安装wps界面中文</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S wps-office-mui-zh-cn</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\"># 卸载wps</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S base-devel</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h3 id=\"Edge\"><a href=\"#Edge\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Edge\"></a>Edge</h3>   <figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">yay -S base-devel</span><br><span class=\"line\">yay -S microsoft-edge-dev-bin</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"参考地址\"><a href=\"#参考地址\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"参考地址\"></a>参考地址</h2><ol>\n<li><a href=\"https://karobben.github.io/2021/05/13/Linux/manjaro/\">To start with manjaro</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/ArcueidCroft/article/details/105363360\">Manjaro安装与软件硬件基本配置（保姆级）_ArcueidCroft的博客-CSDN博客_manjaro配置</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.buptstu.cn/2021/02/07/Manjaro%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AEQv2ray-SSR/\">Manjaro配置Qv2ray&amp;SSR</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Qv2ray/Qv2ray\">Qv2ray/Qv2ray</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Qv2ray/QvPlugin-SSR/releases\">Releases · Qv2ray/QvPlugin-SSR</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/nangy2514/article/details/93194184#4__49\">Manjaro-Pacman命令详解</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/nangy2514/article/details/93045341\">Manjaro - 环境配置及软件安装卸载记录_写虫师的博客-CSDN博客_manjaro卸载软件</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://blog.csdn.net/liaoshengshi/article/details/40024749\">49条消息) Archlinux命令之软件卸载_如丧-CSDN博客_pacman 卸载</a></li>\n</ol>\n","tags":["Linux"]},{"title":"test","url":"/2021/06/20/test/","content":""},{"title":"Hello World","url":"/2021/06/20/hello-world/","content":"<p>Welcome to <a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">Hexo</a>! This is your very first post. Check <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/\">documentation</a> for more info. If you get any problems when using Hexo, you can find the answer in <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/troubleshooting.html\">troubleshooting</a> or you can ask me on <a href=\"https://github.com/hexojs/hexo/issues\">GitHub</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"Quick-Start\"><a href=\"#Quick-Start\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Quick Start\"></a>Quick Start</h2><h3 id=\"Create-a-new-post\"><a href=\"#Create-a-new-post\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Create a new post\"></a>Create a new post</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo new <span class=\"string\">&quot;My New Post&quot;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/writing.html\">Writing</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Run-server\"><a href=\"#Run-server\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Run server\"></a>Run server</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo server</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/server.html\">Server</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Generate-static-files\"><a href=\"#Generate-static-files\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Generate static files\"></a>Generate static files</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo generate</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/generating.html\">Generating</a></p>\n<h3 id=\"Deploy-to-remote-sites\"><a href=\"#Deploy-to-remote-sites\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Deploy to remote sites\"></a>Deploy to remote sites</h3><figure class=\"highlight bash\"><table><tr><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">$ hexo deploy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>More info: <a href=\"https://hexo.io/docs/one-command-deployment.html\">Deployment</a></p>\n"}]